&lt;a class="ext-link" href="http://knowledgeforge.net/ckan/hg/file/tip/doc/api/version2.rst"&gt;&lt;span class="icon"&gt;â€‹&lt;/span&gt;http://knowledgeforge.net/ckan/hg/file/tip/doc/api/version2.rst&lt;/a&gt;
